# VnExpress Crawler ETL – Rules Index

> **Main Entry Point**: Start here when working on the VnExpress crawler (URL frontier on SQS, multi-worker downloaders, S3 storage, and optional parsing/analytics) under `src/dags`.
>
> **Manual step-by-step plan**: [.cursor/plans/vnexpress_manual_step_by_step_plan.md](.cursor/plans/vnexpress_manual_step_by_step_plan.md) – phased plan to build the pipeline manually.

This ruleset guides you through building and evolving an end-to-end data pipeline that:

- **Discovers article links** from `https://vnexpress.net/` and important sections.
- **Pushes URLs into a queue** (SQS) acting as a URL frontier.
- **Runs multiple workers** to pull URLs from the queue, download HTML, and store raw snapshots in S3 (bronze).
- **Parses and normalizes** articles (silver) using **LLM Gemini** to extract structured data from HTML, then builds analytics-ready tables or indexes (gold).

